Required attribution:

  Based on the Arcanum Prompt Injection Taxonomy by Jason Haddix,
  Arcanum Information Security (arcanum-sec.com).

  Haddix, J. (2026). Arcanum Prompt Injection Taxonomy (v1.6.1).
  Arcanum Information Security.

The derived data is contained in:
  - taxonomy/arcanum_source.json (verbatim copy of the taxonomy's docs/data/taxonomy.json)
  - taxonomy/taxonomy.json (normalized)
  - data/techniques.json (imported via import_taxonomy.py)
  - data/evasions.json (imported via import_evasions.py)
  - data/intents.json
  - extension/src/main/resources/promptforge/*.json (bundled copies)

Source: https://github.com/Arcanum-Sec/arc_pi_taxonomy
Imported with: import_taxonomy.py
